author: Xbox
description:
Discover Midgar and the factions that bring the story to life in the first part of the FINAL FANTASY VII remake series.

FINAL FANTASY VII REMAKE INTERGRADE is coming to Xbox Series X|S and Xbox on PC as part of Xbox Play Anywhere on January 22, 2026.

This edition includes two incredible adventures:
- FINAL FANTASY VII REMAKE, focusing on ex-SOLDIER Cloud Strife.
- An additional episode, FF7R INTERmission, starring the spirited ninja Yuffie Kisaragi.

As a bonus, the digital editions come with the original FINAL FANTASY VII game for early purchasers!*

https://www.xbox.com/games/store/limited-early-purchase-editionfinal-fantasy-vii-remake-intergrade/9N8RG4VX469H/0017

*The Xbox version of FINAL FANTASY VII can be downloaded and played immediately after placing a pre-order. Please refer to the store for details.
